title: 30. The Last Dance: Developing Winning Tendencies Part 3
itunes:title: 30. The Last Dance: Developing Winning Tendencies Part 3
description: Are you being true to yourself? On today's show, Andy and the guys discuss why it's important to be comfortable with yourself for your personal brand, why you should be a voice of encouragement, and the positives that have come from the Covid-19 pandemic.
